  <compounddef id="model_template_page" kind="page">
    <compoundname>model_template_page</compoundname>
    <title>Model Template Guide</title>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Detailed guide for using and extending <ref refid="classmodel__template" kindref="compound">model_template</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<sect1 id="model_template_page_1model_template_intro">
<title>Introduction</title>
<para>The <ref refid="classmodel__template" kindref="compound">model_template</ref> class provides the base interface for machine learning models in AnalysisG. It integrates with PyTorch (LibTorch) for neural network functionality.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="model_template_page_1model_template_structure">
<title>Structure</title>
<para>A model template defines:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Network architecture</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Forward pass logic</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Input/output feature mapping</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="model_template_page_1model_template_example">
<title>Example</title>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="keyword">class<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">MyModel<sp/>:<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">public</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="classmodel__template" kindref="compound">model_template</ref><sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">public</highlight><highlight class="normal">:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>torch::nn::Linear<sp/>fc1,<sp/>fc2,<sp/>fc3;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>MyModel()<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>fc1<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="classmodel__template_1a456e96f75278fed9c8d6f4dbff885e39" kindref="member">register_module</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;fc1&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/>torch::nn::Linear(10,<sp/>64));</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>fc2<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="classmodel__template_1a456e96f75278fed9c8d6f4dbff885e39" kindref="member">register_module</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;fc2&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/>torch::nn::Linear(64,<sp/>64));</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>fc3<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="classmodel__template_1a456e96f75278fed9c8d6f4dbff885e39" kindref="member">register_module</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;fc3&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/>torch::nn::Linear(64,<sp/>1));</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>torch::Tensor<sp/><ref refid="classmodel__template_1ac6d8ddbdaf334cfefbe1e6361fd4ebbb" kindref="member">forward</ref>(<ref refid="structgraph__t" kindref="compound">graph_t</ref>*<sp/>data)</highlight><highlight class="keyword"><sp/>override<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>x<sp/>=<sp/>*data-&gt;<ref refid="structgraph__t_1ae55e7c4ea7a4563757d939a96afb52a3" kindref="member">get_data_node</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;features&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">this</highlight><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>x<sp/>=<sp/>torch::relu(fc1-&gt;forward(x));</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>x<sp/>=<sp/>torch::relu(fc2-&gt;forward(x));</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>x<sp/>=<sp/>torch::sigmoid(fc3-&gt;forward(x));</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordflow">return</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>x;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="model_template_page_1model_template_training">
<title>Training</title>
<para>Models are trained using the optimizer with parameters:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="structoptimizer__params__t" kindref="compound">optimizer_params_t</ref><sp/>params;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">params.learning_rate<sp/>=<sp/>0.001;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">params.epochs<sp/>=<sp/>100;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">params.batch_size<sp/>=<sp/>64;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="classanalysis" kindref="compound">analysis</ref><sp/>ana;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a51e47012fc4522964dbfba5baa89090c" kindref="member">add_model</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="keyword">new</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>MyModel(),<sp/>&amp;params,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;training_run&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
</sect1>
